name: Trying to be me/Anxious
description: Trying to be me/Anxious is a representation of how I feel when trying to figure out who I am. It is filled with heavy anxiety, the fear of being judged, the feeling of self-doom, the motionless. And yet it has some life to it, the colors ever-growing with surety in his eyes for he knows that eventually, he will be colorful. @chiba.arte
